pageTitle: Mink caught on video running across the road in Florida with a snake
description: A tiny mink was caught on video running across the road in Florida with a snake. The video was posted on Facebook and posted to YouTube.
metaDescription: A tiny mink was caught on video running across the road in Florida with a snake. This is an illustration by an <AI>.
topicText:
WATCH: Mink drags snake across road in the Everglades
COPELAND, Fla. – A pair of hikers caught the moment a mink crossed a road carrying a large snake in its mouth in Fakahatchee Strand Preserve State Park.

Mink caught on camera carrying snake in Florida
A mink was caught on camera carrying a snake on a nature trail in Fakahatchee Strand Preserve State Park.
Watch: Rarely seen Everglades mink captures 'giant' snake
A Florida resident has captured extraordinary footage showing an Everglades mink scampering across a road with a large snake.
